    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW M-Division engineering, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag six-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing variable M differential lock, ensuring linear power delivery and exceptional corner-exit traction. The chassis integrity is flawless; the rear subframe mounting points have been inspected and remain factory-perfect, while the suspension retains its original kinematics with zero bushing deflection. Every mechanical component, from the cross-drilled rotors to the stainless-steel exhaust manifold, exhibits concours-level preservation. This is a turn-key, investment-grade machine for the purist who demands mechanical transparency and peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
